:"feminine noun","usage":"merciful(1x), pitiful(1x)"},"H2552":{"id":"H2552","lemma":"חָמַם","translit":"châmam","pron":"khaw-mam'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to be hot (literally or figuratively)","kjv_def":"enflame self, get (have) heat, be (wax) hot, (be, wax) warm (self, at).","pos":"verb"},"H2553":{"id":"H2553","lemma":"חַמָּן","translit":"chammân","pron":"kham-mawn'","derivation":"from H2535 (חַמָּה);","strongs_def":"a sun-pillar","kjv_def":"idol, image.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"image(7x), idol(1x)"},"H2554":{"id":"H2554","lemma":"חָמַס","translit":"châmaç","pron":"khaw-mas'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to be violent; by implication, to maltreat","kjv_def":"make bare, shake off, violate, do violence, take away violently, wrong, imagine wrongfully.","pos":"verb","usage":"violated(1x), wronged(1x)"},"H2555":{"id":"H2555","lemma":"חָמָס","translit":"châmâç","pron":"khaw-mawce'","derivation":"from H2554 (חָמַס);","strongs_def":"violence; by implication, wrong; by meton. unjust gain","kjv_def":"cruel(-ty), damage, false, injustice, [idiom] oppressor, unrighteous, violence (against, done), violent (dealing), wrong.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"violence(39x), violent(7x), cruelty(4x), wrong(3x), false(2x), cruel(1x), damage(1x), injustice(1x), unrighteous(1x)"},"H2556":{"id":"H2556","lemma":"חָמֵץ","translit":"châmêts","pron":"khaw-mates'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to be pungent; i.e. in taste (sour, i.e. literally fermented, or figuratively, harsh), in color (dazzling)","kjv_def":"cruel (man), dyed, be grieved, leavened.","pos":"verb","usage":"leavened(5x), cruel(1x), dyed(1x), grieved(1x)"},"H2557":{"id":"H2557","lemma":"חָמֵץ","translit":"châmêts","pron":"khaw-mates'","derivation":"from H2556 (חָמֵץ);","strongs_def":"ferment, (figuratively) extortion","kjv_def":"leaven, leavened (bread).","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"leaven(5x), leaven(2x)"},"H2558":{"id":"H2558","lemma":"חֹמֶץ","translit